high_descs: Walk to the kitchen stove on your left.
Grab a pot from the stove.
Go to the kitchen sink on your right.
Put the pot in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Place the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Wash a pot and reuse it.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the counter, turn right and walk halfway to the sink, turn left so you are facing the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle on the front right burner of the stove.
Turn completely around, take a step, turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the tea kettle in the sink, fill the sink with water, drain the sink, and pick up the tea kettle.
Turn completely around, walk half way to wall, turn right so you are facing the stove.
Place the tea kettle on the rear right burner on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Rinse and replace one of the tea kettles on the stove.

high_descs: turn to the left, move forward and make a right at the end of the counter, turn to the left and face the stove
pick up the tea kettle on the front right burner
turn to the right and move to the sink
put the tea kettle in to the sink and turn on the water to fill the kettle, turn off the water and pick up the tea kettle
turn around and move to the stove on the right, turn to the right to face the stove
put the tea kettle on the back right burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: put a tea kettle full of water on to the stove
